Ask HN: Which founders tried called calling to sell to their target customers?
text:
Hey folks,

I’m Sascha, Founder of Questmate (https://www.questmate.com) & Scriptable.run (https://www.scriptable.run).

I’d be keen who else here is doing called calls as part of their initial sales efforts. It still seems to work quite well, yet it seems not many are doing it. And if you do it, what kind of strategy / script do you see being most effective?

Ask HN: Do you ever browse HN on the New Comments page?
text:
I'm curious how useful some find it and if I'm missing something on effectively using this page [0]. The comments are out of context, thus not so meaningful as a result, and they will lay on arbitrary articles all mixed together, which further complicates context and train of thought, or even an understanding of what the topic is.

How do you use this page, if you do?
